The paper deals with remote sensing image classification using machine learning classifiers, specifically Gaussian process classifiers. This falls under the broad category of machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of probabilistic methods and variational Bayes, which are common in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). In addition, the paper deals with large-scale data, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) or data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
